commitResults.messageBody:
Current implementation is tailored to AB3 (which will not be applicable
to us)

The description, quick start and FAQ section has been modified according
to our User Guide Draft.

In addition, I have also added the features description for add, task,
archive and exit.

Person: Change the constructor and fields of a Person, so that it is
suitable for our audience.
* Fields such as tags and address are unused and have been removed.
* Additional fields (studentId, moduleCode, telegramHandle) were added.
* Only studentId, name and moduleCode are compulsory fields.
* All fields are currently represented as Strings.

AddCommand/Parser: Modify according to the new Person constructor.

GUI: Adjusted to display all the relevant fields of a student.
* Note that it does not look exactly like our Ui mockup, but can
* further refined next time.
